# Git Push & Versioning (SHA-7)

## ⛔ ANTI-RECURSION (Ouroboros)
- **FORBIDDEN:** Manually updating `APP_COMMIT_VERSION` or any hardcoded SHA in `App.tsx` to match the current `git rev-parse HEAD`. 
- **REASON:** Changing the file changes the Hash → the hash becomes invalid → infinite loop.

## ✅ SOURCE OF TRUTH
- **Production/Build:** Use `__GIT_SHA7__` defined in `konnakol_trainer/vite.config.ts`. 
- **Mechanism:** The SHA is injected dynamically **during `vite build`** via `git rev-parse --short=7 HEAD`.
- **UI Display:** The UI must only consume the value provided by the build tool.

## 🛠️ DEV WORKFLOW
- **Fallback:** Use `'dev'` or a static placeholder in `App.tsx`. 
- **Sync:** Never attempt to sync the dev-placeholder with the Git HEAD manually.
- **Pre-push:** Run `npm run build` inside `konnakol_trainer` to verify SHA injection before `git push`.

